# YouPD UI (SSOTA design system)

## Tokens

- Colors, radius, shadows: `packages/ui/src/styles/globals.css` only.
- Canvas/block palette: `packages/ui/src/lib/style-tokens.ts` (`ColorToken`, `TAILWIND_COLOR_PALETTE`).
- Do not introduce one-off hex/oklch in app components.

## Imports

```tsx
// ✅
import { Button } from "@youpd/ui/components/ui/button";
import { cn } from "@youpd/ui/lib/utils";

// ❌ — do not add new files under apps/*/src/components/ui
import { Button } from "@/components/ui/button";
```

## Style rules

- Primary actions: `Button` variant `default` (coral primary + `shadow-xs`).
- Toolbar / canvas: prefer `ssota-ui` (`ToolbarContainer`, `ToolbarIconButton`).
- Radius: `rounded-md` for controls; match `--radius` (0.75rem), not arbitrary `rounded-lg` on buttons.
- Spacing: `gap-2` / `gap-4` for toolbars; `p-6` for empty/card interiors.
- Icons: Lucide in shared UI; Remix Icon only where YouPD pages already use `@remixicon/react`.

## shadcn

- Registry config: `packages/ui/components.json` (style: **new-york**, cssVariables: true).
- Add components to `packages/ui`, not `apps/web`.

## Storybook

Run `pnpm storybook` (or `pnpm --filter @youpd/ui storybook`) — port **6006**. Add stories under `packages/ui/src/stories/`.

